Waves All Plugins Bundle v9r18 MACOSX

 Over 130 Plugins | Easy Activation | 64-Bit Support




Changes - Waves V9r18



- The new Vitamin Sonic Enhancer available separately as well as in Mercury,
  Horizon, Diamond, Platinum, Gold, Pro Show, SD7 Pro Show, Essentials and Prelude.
- WLM Loudness Meter is added to the list of single plugins (in addition to WLM Plus).
- Manny Marroquin Distortion: minor sound related fix.




V9 System Requirements

CPU
Core Duo 2.3Ghz

RAM
4 GB

Operating System
10.7 - 10.9.2
OS X 10.9 Mavericks

Screen Resolution
1024x768







[Installation]

-> UnZip

-> Run installer

-> Choose items to install


Bundles to select:

- Mercury
- GTR Solo
- SSL 4000 collection
- Video Sound Suite (for more IR's)


Singles to select:

- AbbeyRoad Kings Mics
- AbbeyRoad J37
- AbbeyRoad ReelADT
- AbbeyRoad RS56
- Waves Tune LT


-> Install

-> Run Waves_R9_Patch.command (this will open the terminal)

-> Run waves AU reg utility 9.2 (is in waves folder - waveshells)

-> FINISHED


To uninstall previous versions do the following:

1. Delete the Waves folder located at Mac HD > Applications.

2. Delete the Waves Preferences folder located at Mac HD > Users > Your User > Library > Preferences.


3. Delete any Waveshells from the following locations:

Mac HD > Library > Application Support > Digidesign > Plug-Ins
Mac HD > Library > Audio > Plug-Ins > Components
Mac HD > Library > Audio > Plug-Ins > MAS
Mac HD > Library > Audio > Plug-Ins > VST
Mac HD > Library > Audio > Plug-Ins > VST3
Mac HD > Library > Application Support > Waves

4. Empty Trash.
